<p>
rufo celebrates pagan men, pantheists. he has been inspired by the mosaics, tomb paintings and heroic statuary of the greco-roman world. those ancient days when young roman men and boy slaves, the <i> concubinus</i>, openly messed around. when hadrian loved antinoüs. when the <i>satyricon</i> was a best-seller and same-sex marriages were cool.</td>
