<b>There's the jocks that are worn and there’s the jocks who wear them. both seem to perform better when well worn-in and covered in sweat, clinging tightly and offering that all-important support.<p>
<p>
the jockstrap is an essential ingredient in locker room mysticism. putting one on for the first time is an initiation ritual — a coming of age ceremony for a growing boy who’s suddenly put on some weight between his legs.
<p>
it’s a truly primal bonding experience when a bunch of guys strip buck naked and tug on a tight, stretchy pouch that they never wear outside the gym. or do they? (gee, buddy, all my shorts were in the laundry.)<br>

