<HEAD>
<title>men in their underwear · high school confidential: showers</title>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#5AAAE0" LINK="#D0AD71" VLINK="#D0AD71" ALINK="#FFFFFF">


<BODY><br>
<blockquote>
<TABLE WIDTH=227 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=5>
