<font face="times, times new roman" size=4 color="#ffffff"><b><i>
‘today you can express freely a male sensuality and all the universes which it implies, through photos, drawings and movies. this has not always been possible in centuries dominated by the cult of female sensuality.’<p>
<a href="dupre_sailor.html"><img src="dupre_sailor.jpg" width=200 height=114 align=bottom vspace=0 border=0 hspace=0></a><p>
