<img src="dragon_head.gif" width=250 height=301 align=bottom vspace=0 hspace=0 border=0><p>
<font face="arial, helvetica" size=2>
<a href="dragon_3.html"><img src="dragon3_sm.jpg" width=135 height=179 align=left vspace=1 hspace=0 border=0></a>
<br><br><FONT COLOR="#DCA700"><b>by kyle<p>
<font color="#CD294A">on location in<br>west hollywood<br><br><FONT COLOR="#A837A1">okay. it’s saturday night at probe in west hollywood, california and critical mass is setting in. like, i’m already the music, okay? and there’s these hot muscleboys workin’ up mega-sweat. not sure what time it is... like i care.<p>
<a href="dragon_6.html"><img src="dragon6_sm.jpg" width=84 height=172 align=right vspace=0 hspace=0 border=0></a> 
okay. up on the boxes, where the showboyz are showin’ it to the boyz, they’ve got these dudes dancin’ and showin’ off straps and thongs and stuff from raymond dragon’s store over on santa monica boulevard. <a href="dragon_5.html"><img src="dragon5_sm.jpg" width=100 height=245 align=left vspace=2 hspace=0 border=0></a>i got to meet raymond dragon a few minutes ago. cool dude, like from michigan and not old or anything. he makes totally cool stuff which i like cause the fabric is so hot — stretchy, fits real cool.<p>
me? i’m stripped down to these hot black boxers and feelin’ pretty good about myself. so check out dragon’s store in wee-ho — or his place in new york. or call 1-800-247-5168 to find out where they sell his stuff elsewhere. here’s some pix i took. dragon makes lots more than this, though. i ran outta film. gotta go. later.</b></td></table>
