<HEAD>
<title>BERSERKISTAN IN BOSNIA: Odd Anderson, Photographer</title>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#454545" link="#A62A2A" vlink="#B87333">

<BODY>
<blockquote>
<img src="flat280.gif" height=119 width=280 align=bottom alt=BERSERKISTAN><br>
<center>
<hr size=1 align=left>
<p><br><br>
<img src="odd4.gif" width=217 height=320 hspace=0 align=bottom border=1><br><br>
<FONT SIZE=5><font color= "#5e5a80"><b>Odd Anderson</b><br>
