<DOCHDR>
http://main.linder.com:80/berserk/tough.html 204.80.101.215 19970217122816 text/html 10120
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:24:20 GMT
