<title>BERSERKISTAN IN BOSNIA: Amps, Skins & Strings</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#454545" link="#B87333" alink=#ff0000" vlink="#B87333">
<blockquote>
<BODY>

<center>
<br><br>
