http://main.linder.com:80/berserk/blahs.html 204.80.101.215 19970217123230 text/html 10504
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:28:35 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 12-Nov-96 16:46:58 GMT
