<a href="http://www.army.mil/">America's Army</a> The US Army Home Page<br>
<a href="http://www.army.mil/">America's Army in Bosnia</a> The US Army in Bosnia<br>
<a href="http://www.usmc.mil/">Marine Link</a> The United States Marine Corps<br>
<a href="http://www.nato.int/">NATO</a> Official World Wide Web page<br>
