<a href="http://embassy.org/wwbosnia/wwbosnia.html">Women for Women in Bosnia</a><br>
<a href="http://foghorn.usfca.edu/archives/fall.95/f09/features/tactic.html">Rape Used as a Tactic</a> Fact sheet provided by Women for Women in Bosnia<br>
<a href="http://suc.suc.org/politics/rape/raskovic/main.html">Serbian Women Victims of War</a> Dr. Sanda Raskovic<br>
<a href="http://www.csv.warwick.ac.uk/~esrhi/bosrap.html">The Rape of Bosnia</a> Systematic Rape in Bosnia<br>
