<p><font size=2>
<FORM method=GET action="http://altavista.digital.com/cgi-bin/query">
<INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=pg VALUE=q>
At Berserkistan, you can search the <INPUT TYPE=radio NAME=what
VALUE=web CHECKED>Web or <INPUT TYPE=radio NAME=what
VALUE=news>News Groups<br><font size=2> 
and display the results as <INPUT TYPE=radio
NAME=fmt VALUE=c>Compact or <INPUT TYPE=radio NAME=fmt VALUE=d CHECKED>Detailed output.<br>
