<DOCHDR>
http://main.linder.com:80/berserk/federation_727.html 204.80.101.215 19970217142640 text/html 7789
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 14:22:33 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 12-Nov-96 17:37:05 GMT
Content-length: 7600
