<DOCHDR>
http://main.linder.com:80/berserk/sreb_women_713.html 204.80.101.215 19970217140130 text/html 8806
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 13:57:38 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 13-Nov-96 23:08:50 GMT
